<plot>The story about the man who did not fear Mike Tyson. This is the story of a Danish boxer's meeting with one of the world's most famous boxer. In an in-depth portrait we get under the skin of the IBC world-boxing champion, 'Super' Brian Nielsen, who in his 63 professional fights against such giants as Tony Tubbs, Larry Holmes and Orlin Norris has only been defeated twice.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?136555</url></doc>
